A keyword query string for this index.

Translate user intent into likely index terms (titles, descriptions, tags, genres, subjects), not a long natural sentence.
Prefer short keyword phrases.

Examples of translation:
- "items of interest to medical people" -> "nurse hospital medical healthcare"
- "funny and action movies" -> "comedy action"
- "wartime hospital scenes" -> "war hospital nurse"

If the first search returns no results, try broader or adjacent keywords before giving up.
Use an empty string "" only when the user wants a pure sort with no keyword constraint.
